<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>마이페이지</title>
        <script src="/mypage.mjs" type="module"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/mypage.css" />
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200"
        />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mypage-header">
                <h1 class="title" id="title">마이페이지</h1>
                <button class="admin-button" id="admin-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">admin_panel_settings</span>
                    관리자 페이지
                </button>
                <button class="logout-button" id="logout-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">logout</span>
                    로그아웃
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="profile-image-container">
                    <div class="profile-image" id="profile-image">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-image-actions">
                        <button class="image-upload-button" id="image-upload-button">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">photo_camera</span>
                            사진 변경
                        </button>
                        <button class="image-delete-button" id="image-delete-button">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">delete</span>
                            사진 삭제
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <input type="file" id="profile-image-input" accept="image/*" style="display: none;" />
                </div>
                
                <div class="profile-info">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <label>아이디</label>
                        <div class="info-value" id="userid">로딩 중...</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <label>닉네임</label>
                        <div class="info-value" id="username">로딩 중...</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <label>이메일</label>
                        <div class="info-value" id="email">로딩 중...</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <label>소개</label>
                        <div class="info-value" id="description">소개가 없습니다.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <label>가입일</label>
                        <div class="info-value" id="created-at">로딩 중...</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <label>UID</label>
                        <div class="info-value" id="uid">로딩 중...</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <button class="edit-button" onclick="location.href='/mypage/edit'">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">edit</span>
                    프로필 수정
                </button>
                <button class="password-button" onclick="location.href='/mypage/edit/password'">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">lock</span>
                    비밀번호 변경
                </button>
                <button class="delete-account-button" id="delete-account-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">delete_forever</span>
                    계정 삭제
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="notice-container"></div>
        
        <div class="modal-overlay" id="delete-modal-overlay" style="display: none;">
            <div class="modal">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h3>계정 삭제 확인</h3>
                    <button class="modal-close" id="modal-close">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">close</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>정말로 계정을 삭제하시겠습니까?</p>
                    <p class="warning">이 작업은 되돌릴 수 없습니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button class="cancel-button" id="cancel-delete">취소</button>
                    <button class="confirm-delete-button" id="confirm-delete">삭제</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html> 